function goToTop(){$("html,body").animate({scrollTop:0},"slow")}function scrollBtn(){$(this).scrollTop()>550?$(".goToTopBtn").fadeIn():$(".goToTopBtn").fadeOut()}function numberWithCommas(e){return e.toString().replace(/\B(?=(\d{3})+(?!\d))/g,",")}function convertMinsToHrsMins(e){let a=Math.floor(e/60),n=e%60;return n=n<10?""+n:n,(a=a<10?""+a:a)>1?a+" Hours  And "+n+" Minutes":a+" Hour  And "+n+" Minutes"}function changeMonthName(e,a){if(1==a)switch(e){case 0:monthName="January";break;case 1:monthName="February";break;case 2:monthName="March";break;case 3:monthName="April";break;case 4:monthName="May";break;case 5:monthName="June";break;case 6:monthName="July";break;case 7:monthName="August";break;case 8:monthName="September";break;case 9:monthName="October";break;case 10:monthName="November";break;case 11:monthName="December"}else switch(e){case 0:monthName="Jan";break;case 1:monthName="Feb";break;case 2:monthName="March";break;case 3:monthName="April";break;case 4:monthName="May";break;case 5:monthName="June";break;case 6:monthName="July";break;case 7:monthName="Aug";break;case 8:monthName="Sep";break;case 9:monthName="Oct";break;case 10:monthName="Nov";break;case 11:monthName="Dec"}}function changeDayName(e){switch(e){case 1:case 21:case 31:dayName=e+"st";break;case 2:case 22:dayName=e+"nd";break;case 3:case 23:dayName=e+"rd";break;default:dayName=e+"th"}}function hasClass(e,a){return new RegExp(" "+a+" ").test(" "+e.className+" ")}function addClass(e,a){hasClass(e,a)||(e.className+=" "+a)}function removeClass(e,a){var n=" "+e.className.replace(/[\t\r\n]/g," ")+" ";if(hasClass(e,a)){for(;n.indexOf(" "+a+" ")>=0;)n=n.replace(" "+a+" "," ");e.className=n.replace(/^\s+|\s+$/g,"")}}function toggleClass(e,a){var n=" "+e.className.replace(/[\t\r\n]/g," ")+" ";if(hasClass(e,a)){for(;n.indexOf(" "+a+" ")>=0;)n=n.replace(" "+a+" "," ");e.className=n.replace(/^\s+|\s+$/g,"")}else e.className+=" "+a}function removePopup(e){$(document).mouseup(function(a){e.is(a.target)&&0===e.has(a.target).length&&(e.hide(),a.stopPropagation(),$(document).off("mouseup"))})}function closeCurrentPopup(e){$($(e)[0].parentElement.parentElement.parentElement).hide()}function backColor(e,a){$(e).css("border",a)}function capitalize(e){try{if(e.includes(" and "))e=e.replace(" and "," And ");else if(e.includes("(and "))e=e.replace("(and ","(And ");else if(null==e||""==e)return;e=e.split(" ");for(var a=0;a<e.length;a++)e[a]=e[a][0].toUpperCase()+e[a].substr(1);return e.join(" ")}catch(e){}}
